text: Reimu Hakurei: Well, well, well... I'm not surprised to find you here
Reimu Hakurei: Even if you're not a ghost, you should watch your weight
Yuyuko Saigyouji: Oh, hello there! I appreciate your concern!
Yuyuko Saigyouji: Don't worry, I'll be fine.
Yuyuko Saigyouji: You should watch yourself, always crisped...
Reimu Hakurei: For what reason! This night has been a pain...
Reimu Hakurei: I cannot sleep, this festival has gone throughout all the night!
Yuyuko Saigyouji: Then you should have played with us all long!
Reimu Hakurei: I need sleep to protect Gensokyo.
Yuyuko Saigyouji: You should protect your mood!
Reimu Hakurei: Thank you, but I won't protect Gensokyo out of sheer happiness
Yuyuko Saigyouji: Too bad. I still want to have some fun, though.
Yuyuko Saigyouji: I can't let you stop this festival yet.
Reimu Hakurei: I will try, nonetheless.
